Privacy Policy
LAST UPDATED ON 9TH OF December, 2023

We know you care about your personal information and we take your privacy seriously. Please read the following to learn more about our Privacy Policy.

Collection of data
Reedroux only collects data that is required to provide services to you. None of the collected data can be used to personally identify a user/individual.

Saved data
The following information is saved by Reedroux only for proper function of them:

User Ids ( For user specific features, such as profile level and vote rewards )

Channel Ids ( For configurations that are specific to channels )

Role Ids ( For the dj roles feature configuration )

Server Ids ( For server settings and preferences )

Any user supplied content that can include profile backgrounds, custom stations, stage topic

Security of data
We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with your requested service. What data we do collect, weâ€™ll protect using commercially reasonable means to prevent loss and theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use, or modification.

Link to other sites
Our service may link to external sites that are not operated by us. Please be aware that we have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.

Opting out
Users can always opt-out simply by stopping using Reedroux or kicking it from their server. Upon request, users may also request to have all of their current data deleted from Reedroux.

Contact us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy policies, please contact us on our [support server](https://discord.gg/evGhPdRJWH), and we will try to resolve your concerns.
